title.narrative: HEALTH NORTH SYRIA

description.narrative: Syria's conflict-affected population have their critical health needs met, in line with the HRP and as part of the UNICEF JOP, which contributes to Child Health, Immunization, Immunization (Covid), Maternal And Newborn Health, Maternal And Newborn Health (Covid), Other Cross-Sectoral Programme Areas. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: MENARO delivers timely, equitable and principled humanitarian action as a complement to country office-led operations where required, including through the cross-border component of the Syria programmes as part of the Whole of Syria response.
